  "summary": "Enables an authoring interface on a Course page with inline controls for editing, managing sections and activities, bulk actions, and an Activity Chooser modal for adding activities and resources.",
  "where_it_fits": "This module is activated on a Course Page (reached via My Courses or Dashboard \u2192 select course) and switches the course view into edit mode for content creation and organization; it is primarily used by teachers during course setup and ongoing content edits (the Settings tab is visible to teachers).",
  "assumed_state_on_entry": "Logged in as a user with editing/teacher permissions and currently viewing an existing Course Page."
